#

Cucumber Lemonade

10 min
$3.5
50 kcal
Difficulty: 5%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

BeverageRefreshingSummer Drink

Description

A refreshing and hydrating drink with the crispness of cucumber and the zing of lemon, perfect for hot days!

Ingredients

  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • lemon juice: 1/2 cup
  • water: 4 cups
  • sugar: 1/4 cup
  • mint leaves: a handful (for garnish)
